grootevent - Desktop Manager
----------------------------

Infos for xml catalog files -> http://www.xmlsoft.org/catalog.html

set --sysconfdir=<path> to /etc or other xml-catalog!!

Be sure to use a recent metacity (or use the patch)
and deactivate Nautilus to manage the background!

A patch for older metacity version could be found on 
the berlios project site:

https://developer.berlios.de/projects/grootevent/

